        },
        {
            "title": "天水圍居屋業主為返內地退休 賣樓套現278萬元 持貨26年勁賺逾4倍！",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jUxWWT8Wijkz5zJ3zHEglw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcyMA--/https://media.zenfs.com/vi/28hse_com_210/315ab56fcdc2eaa2ac45d1e79d89f23a\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A9%E6%B0%B4%E5%9C%8D%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B%E6%A5%AD%E4%B8%BB%E7%82%BA%E8%BF%94%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%80%80%E4%BC%91-%E8%B3%A3%E6%A8%93%E5%A5%97%E7%8F%BE278%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83-%E6%8C%81%E8%B2%A826%E5%B9%B4%E5%8B%81%E8%B3%BA%E9%80%BE4%E5%80%8D-053309749.html",
